{"tid":567123,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Christopher Nolan 親口否認將執導第 25 部《007》電影","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T13:20:43.000Z","uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1094563a15840466068e81149e6bb0ae5fec22ef","tid":567123,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"知名諜報電影《007》先前確認 Daniel Craig 將會繼續出演 James Bond 一角，並傳出了副標題將會叫做《Shatterhead》，故事改編自 1999 年的原著小說《Never Dream Of Dying》。此外還傳出驚人消息，電影系列製作人 Barbara Broccoli 竟在訪問時提出 James Bond 有可能改為女性演員出演的可能性，造成廣大影迷爭相議論。<br />\n<br />\n先前被傳出有機會執導第 25 部《007》電影的名導 Christopher Nolan，直到近日接受 BBC Radio 4 的 Desert Island Discs 節目中，親口否認他為第 25 部《007》電影的導演，但也順勢表達他對於《007》的熱愛。相信影迷也希望有朝一日，能看到這位知名英國大導接下《007》電影導演一職，延續 James Bond 的傳奇故事。<br />\n<br />\nI won&rsquo;t be the man. No, categorically. I think every time they hire a new director I&rsquo;m rumoured to be doing it.<br />\n<br />\nI&rsquo;d love to make a Bond film at some point and I think those producers &ndash; Barbara and Michael &ndash; they do a tremendous job and Sam Mendes has done a terrific job the last couple of films, so they don&rsquo;t particularly need me. But I&rsquo;ve always been inspired by the films and would love to do one someday.<br />\n<br />\nI love the character, I love the films, I&rsquo;ve been very inspired by the films as anyone who&rsquo;s seen my films will find embarrassingly obvious. But you&rsquo;d only take on a franchise like that if you could bring something completely new to it, if that were needed. And I think at the moment they&rsquo;re doing fantastically well without me.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/2/james-bond-25-director-christopher-nolan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F2%2Fjames-bond-25-director-christopher-nolan&d=LG5iZRcf1akFTiRMjndvraWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=92fff52f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/2/james-bond-25-director-christopher-nolan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d172037d6f59177e265f1cd383950d8024fb9b80","tid":567123,"uid":110112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"咁佢幾時拍新戲"},{"pid":"066c94442b738fac255da8e838da1ec2165b9bcd","tid":567123,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"想睇佢拍 將007拍成懸疑片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0108a179906859e331f4d39a97cd79569fc560fd","tid":567123,"uid":44674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"諗起skyfall 個奸角擺明係老翻小丑就覺得好笑"},{"pid":"bedef98bf570a69b16c8ceda8d9d37494bd25003","tid":567123,"uid":19613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"唔好係黑人就ok, 完全唔match 007"},{"pid":"94d8b2d28df3a750f55fd8f38c573c80395b55ca","tid":567123,"uid":13946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"如果係佢拍<br />\n會有IMAX<br />\n壯觀華麗視覺效果+非線性故仔+偏冷色調<br />\n007會亦正亦邪<br />\n佛地魔會死，米高堅頂上<br />\nCillian Murphy多數會係奸唔曬嘅奸角<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49daa94927f944e2ba74e4bd54c814f0aed0833f","tid":567123,"uid":13885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94d8b2d28df3a750f55fd8f38c573c80395b55ca","tid":567123,"uid":13946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"如果係佢拍<br />\n會有IMAX<br />\n壯觀華麗視覺效果+非線性故仔+偏冷色調<br />\n007會亦正亦邪<br />\n佛地魔會死，米高堅頂上<br />\nCillian Murphy多數會係奸唔曬嘅奸角<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"Murphy 